    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document discusses the applicability of Constraint-Based LSP Setup using LDP.  It discusses possible network applications, extensions to Label Distribution Protocol (LDP) required to implement constraint-based routing, guidelines for deployment and known limitations of the protocol.  This document is a prerequisite to advancing CR-LDP on the standards track.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
